  "_about": {
    "purpose": "Curated pin maps for RF components in data/sample_components.json. Each entry lists the authoritative pin assignments from the manufacturer datasheet so tools/pin_map.py can validate LLM-emitted schematic_data against reality instead of letting invented pin numbers (e.g. DATA/CTRL/GPIO1 on an SOT-89) ship.",
    "sources": "All entries cross-checked against manufacturer datasheets. References: www.analog.com, www.ti.com, www.macom.com, www.qorvo.com.",
